marketing: Shell Naturelle S2 Grease  A600P 1.5 is a high performance fully biodegradable grease for use on open gears, wire ropes and cables. This product is formulated with renewable base fluids and contains a select blend of additives to offer corrosion resistance and high load carrying performance. Shell Naturelle S2 Grease  A600P 1.5 offers high resistance to water wash off due to its outstanding adhesion properties.
